== By the author ==

At~the end of~this little free story what Luwrain is,
me would like to write a~few words as~some kind of~personal notes.
I had~to use screen readers since 2001 and never from that moment was satisfied with them.
However, me strongly convinced that they are a~great achievement and Luwrain will never try to~dispute their value.
It~would be~nice if everybody will consider Luwrain just as~an~attempt to~create something new,
hopefully, interesting and useful in~areas, which previously didn't get enough attention.
Besides that, me is very grateful to~all [[http://emacspeak.sourceforge.net  emacspeak]] authors 
because the~results of~their work gave me a~reliable tool  and a~lot of~useful thoughts!

With best wishes, [[http://marigostra.com/ Michael Pozhidaev]].

